---
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page
  title="About | Botify Life"
  description="Learn more about Botify Life, our mission, and how we help you improve your lifestyle with automation and AI."
  pageUrl="/about"
>
  <main
    class="bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-50 to-white min-h-screen pb-12 px-4"
  >
    <!-- Banner Section -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center py-16">
      <h2
        class="text-lg font-mono text-blue-600 mb-2 tracking-wider uppercase text-center"
      >
        Our Mission
      </h2>
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-center mb-6 text-gray-900"
        style="font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'sans-serif';"
      >
        Empower people to achieve more with AI.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg text-center mb-8 max-w-2xl">
        We believe in unlocking human creativity and productivity by integrating
        AI into everyday work. Botify helps teams and individuals transform the
        way they operate, making AI a practical and valuable part of every
        workflow.
      </p>
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2678468/pexels-photo-2678468.jpeg"
        alt="Team collaborating in office"
        class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full max-w-2xl object-cover"
      />
    </section>
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-8 mt-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        About Botify Life
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-10 text-center">
        Botify Life empowers individuals and businesses to boost productivity
        and creativity through automation, AI, and customizable bots. Our
        platform is designed for everyone—from beginners to experts—to unlock
        the full potential of AI in daily workflows.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col">
          <h2
            class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye text-indigo-400"></i>
            Our Mission
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We make advanced automation and AI accessible to everyone. Our tools
            help you create, manage, and scale bots and agents so you can
            achieve more with less effort.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col">
          <h2
            class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <i class="fa-solid fa-gift text-indigo-400"></i>
            What We Offer
          </h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 ml-2">
            <li>Easy-to-use platform for MCP servers and agents</li>
            <li>Flexible pricing for every stage</li>
            <li>LLM usage: pay per token or use your own API key</li>
            <li>Professional support & growing community</li>
            <li>Earn by creating and selling your own bots and servers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col">
          <h2
            class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <i class="fa-solid fa-coins text-indigo-400"></i>
            Opportunity for Earning
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Create and sell your own MCP servers and agents. Keep 80% of your
            earnings—Botify only charges a 20% commission. Build your business
            while empowering others!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-6 shadow flex flex-col">
          <h2
            class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star text-indigo-400"></i>
            Why Choose Botify Life?
          </h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 ml-2">
            <li>Modern, accessible, and responsive design</li>
            <li>Transparent pricing & flexible billing</li>
            <li>Focus on privacy, security, and user empowerment</li>
            <li>Continuous updates and new features</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Page>
